in the early 1500s,

00:00:11.174 --> 00:00:14.010
the coast of Southeast Asia is marked 
with a message

00:00:14.010 --> 00:00:16.429
that has since become iconic:

00:00:16.971 --> 00:00:19.599
Here be dragons.

